content.rendered:
Directed by Merlapaka Gandhi.

Written by Merlapaka Gandhi. Sheik Dawood G.. Merlapaka Gandhi. Rishabh Purohit.

Cast Sharwanand(Express Raja). Surabhi(Amulya). Urvashi(Veerabhadramma). Krishna Murali Posani(CI Pratap). Harish Uthaman(Kesava Reddy). Surya(Surya). Nagineedu(Rama Murthy). Brahmaji(Bill Gates). Prabhas Sreenu(Seenu). Supreet(Binami British).Shakalaka Shankar. Sapthagiri(Sapthagiri). Dhanraj(Inumu) . Mahesh Achanta(Smoker).Anand Bharathi. Ajay Ghosh(Ajay Ghosh).Kalpalatha. Raghu Kumar Karumanchi(Subramanyam). Kadambari Kiran(Pet Shop Owner). Duvvasi Mohan(Machine). Narasimha(Dictionary Seller).Vanukuri Narayanswami.Suresh Phani.Viswa Raghu.T.S. Sastry.Edward Sunny.Vaibhav Surya.Ashok Vardhan

Language Telugu.

Producers V. Vamsi Krishna Reddy. N. Sundeep. Pramod Uppalapati.

Production Goldmines Telefilms. UV Creations.
